---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title='Terms of Service'
  description='terms of service'
  crawl={true}
>
  <div class='lg:container lg:mx-auto'>
    <section class='flex flex-col gap-4 px-5 py-16'>
      <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold'>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class='text-lg'><em>Last updated: 21.08.2025</em></p>

      <h2 class='text-3xl font-semibold'>⚠️ Important Notice</h2>
      <p class='text-lg italic font-semibold'>
        FjordBoost is not a real company. This website and its
        content are part of a school project created for educational
        purposes only. The services described on this site (such as
        SEO, digital optimisation, and consultancy) are fictional
        and not actually offered. No commercial activity, sales, or
        client engagements are carried out through this website.
      </p>
      <p class='text-lg'>
        By continuing to view this site, you acknowledge that it is
        a learning exercise only and not a commercial service.
      </p>

      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>
        1. Educational Purpose Only
      </h2>
      <p class='text-lg'>
        The FjordBoost website exists solely as a school project and
        does not represent a real business. All descriptions of
        services, client outcomes, and testimonials are part of the
        project brief and are not factual or available for purchase.
      </p>

      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>2. Use of the Website</h2>
      <ul class='text-lg list-disc list-inside'>
        <li>
          You may browse this site for educational or illustrative
          purposes only.
        </li>
        <li>
          No part of this project may be used for commercial
          purposes.
        </li>
        <li>
          All content (text, graphics, and logos) was created or
          adapted for educational demonstration and is not intended
          for real-world business use.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>3. No Services Offered</h2>
      <p class='text-lg'>
        FjordBoost does not provide SEO services, audits,
        consultancy, or digital marketing in reality. Any references
        to clients, case studies, or results are fictionalised
        examples created as part of the project.
      </p>

      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>4. No Liability</h2>
      <p class='text-lg'>
        Since FjordBoost is not a real company, no liability,
        warranty, or responsibility is accepted for the use of the
        information presented. This website should not be relied
        upon for actual SEO advice, strategy, or business decisions.
      </p>

      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>5. Governing Context</h2>
      <p class='text-lg'>
        This project was created for educational purposes in [insert
        school/university/course name]. These Terms are intended
        only to clarify the fictional and non-commercial nature of
        this project.
      </p>

      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>6. Contact</h2>
      <p class='text-lg'>
        Any contact details displayed on this site (email, phone,
        address) are placeholders and should not be used to attempt
        contact.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
